{"type":"message","id":"141b064a","parentId":"58abc2b6","timestamp":"2026-06-01T03:10:08.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a6v78q6p2674_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780283408002}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f4b5b92","parentId":"141b064a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T03:10:17.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time is Monday, June 1st, 2026, 11:10 AM (Asia/Shanghai). \n\n- 11:10 is within work hours (9:30-11:30), so I should check for reminders.\n- It's 11:10, which is near 10:30 (water reminder) - actually it's past 10:30, but since we're in the 9:30-11:30 window, I should check if there's a water reminder to send. 11:10 is past the 10:30 window... but it's still within 9:30-11:30. The HEARTBEAT.md says \"10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近\" - so it's not exactly at those times, it's near them. 11:10 is past 10:30 but still in the morning work period. I'll send a water reminder since it's close enough to 10:30.\n- It's Monday, so no weekend check needed.\n- No specific long-sitting reminder at this exact time (would need to track cumulative time).\n- Not Friday 17:00.\n\nIt's Monday 11:10, within morning work hours. Should remind about water since 10:30 passed but is within the window. Also check for long sitting. Let me keep it brief and friendly. I don't have context about when the user last drank water or sat down, but since this is the first heartbeat of the day around this time, I'll give a short water reminder.\n\nLet me reply with HEARTBEAT_OK since it's borderline. Actually the time is 11:10 which is past the 10:30 window (should be near 10:30 ±30 min or so). It's a bit far from 10:30 now. I'll keep it minimal. Actually, let me just send a quick water reminder - better to remind than not."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n💧 喝口水吧，10点多那会儿应该还没来得及喝。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780283408004}}
